h3. Summary

When updating an issue's Parent Link thru {{PUT /rest/api/2/issue/<issueKey>?overrideScreenSecurity=true&overrideEditableFlag=true&notifyUsers=false}}, where the "Parent Link" field is hidden from the Edit screen, an Internal Server Error is returned.

*Steps to replicate*
# Install Jira Portfolio
# Create Hierarchy (e.g. see screenshot)
# Create a several Parents (mine is Initiative)
# Create Child issue (mine is task) and set Parent Link
# Hide "Parent Link" from Edit Issue screen (see screenshot)
# Create Connect App with the following call, with {{customfield_10015}} as the Parent Link's customefield ID (this varies from instance to instance)
{code}
httpClient.put({
    url: `https://new-test-anne.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/SCRUM-6?overrideScreenSecurity=true&overrideEditableFlag=true&notifyUsers=false`,
    contentType: 'application/json',
    json: true,
    body:{"fields":{"customfield_10015":"SCRUM-4"}}
}, (error, res, body) => {
    console.log(JSON.stringify(error, null, 2));
    console.log(JSON.stringify(body, null, 2));
    console.log(JSON.stringify(res, null, 2));
});
{code}
